The paper focuses on improving machine learning fairness, which is a topic related to both machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The sensitive fields mentioned in the abstract, such as criminal justice and loan decision, are also related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). Additionally, the use of adversarial networks is a common technique in deep learning, which falls under the category of signal processing (cs.SI).
